channel.title: List of items you can merch
channel.description:
Here is a list of items you can merch I suggest you BUY BUY BUY
[b]Diamonds [1k each] and other gems![/b] - People are finally getting into the diamond(e) bolts selling at 1k each.. time to take the profit out of the fletchers hands.
[b]Birds Nest [1k each][/b] -Advertise here and there, people don't know the price. 1k each is an easy flip at w1 varrock.
[b]Tree Seeds [/b] -How how people don't know what a palm tree seed is worth. Lots of seeds are undervalued and are an easy flip. If you get any yew or magic tree seeds, hit me up.
[b]Ores[/b] -What a wonderful resource at a low price.. why is it low? The market will catch up..
That's all I am putting forward atm and I have made a great deal of money with each of these categories so I know it can be done.
